quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) ntitwa- kwaguriye igituza
  94,2,Tukanagutura umutwaro (tukoro- hereza gusohoza ubutumwa)
  94,3,Wari ukuremereye umugongo
  94,4,Tukanamenyekanisha izina ryawe
  94,5,"Mu by’ukuri, nyuma y’ingorane haza ibihe byiza"
  94,6,"Rwose, nyuma y’ingorane haza ibihe byiza"
  94,7,"Bityo nuhuguka, ujye ushishikara (mu gusenga Allah)"
  94,8,Kandi (imigambi n’ibyiringiro byawe) ujye ubitura Nyagasani wawe (wenyine)
  95,1,Ndahiriye ku giti cy’umutini n’icy’umuzeti
  95,2,No ku Musozi wa Sinayi
  95,3,No kuri uyu mujyi utekanye (Maka)
  95,4,"Mu by’ukuri, twaremye umuntu mu ishusho ryiza"
  95,5,Hanyuma tumushyira ku rwego rwo hasi cyane (ageze mu zabukuru atagishoboye kugira icyo yimarira)
  95,6,"Ariko abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza (n’iyo bageze mu zabukuru, hari ibikorwa byo kwiyegereza Imana bakomeza gukora); abo bazagororerwa ibihembo bidashira (Ijuru)"
  95,7,"Nonese nyuma y’ibyo (yewe muntu), ni iki kigutera guhakana umunsi w’ibihembo"
  95,8,Ese Allah si we Mucamanza usumba abandi
  96,1,Soma ku izina rya Nyagasani wawe waremye (ibiriho byose)
  96,2,Yaremye umuntu mu rusoro rw’amaraso
  96,3,Soma! Kandi Nyagasani wawe ni Umunyacyubahiro uhebuje
  96,4,We wigishije (umuntu kwandika) akoresheje ikaramu
  96,5,Yigishije umuntu ibyo atari azi
  96,6,"Oya! Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ararengera (arahakana kandi agakora ibibi)"
  96,7,Iyo amaze kubona ko yihagije (kubera ibyo atunze)
  96,8,"Mu by’ukuri, (umenye ko) kwa Nyagasani wawe ari ho garukiro"
  96,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) wabonye wawundi (Abu Jahl) ubuza
  96,10,Umugaragu (wacu Muhamadi) gusenga
  96,11,Ese yabuza ate (umugaragu wacu) aramutse ari mu nzira y’ukuri
  96,12,"Cyangwa ari gukangurira (abantu) gukora ibyiza, (mbwira icyaba iherezo ry’umubuza)"
  96,13,Ngaho mbwira (Abu Jahl) aramutse ahinyura (ukuri) akanatera umugongo
  96,14,Ese ntabwo azi ko Allah abona (ibyo akora)
  96,15,"Oya! Natarekera aho, tuzamufata uruhanga rwe turukururire mu muriro"
  96,16,"Uruhanga rubeshya, rw’urunyabyaha"
  96,17,Ngaho nahamagare abambari be
  96,18,Natwe tuzahamagara (abamalayika bacu) barinda umuriro (bamukanire urumukwiye)
  96,19,"Oya! (Yewe Muhamadi), ntukamwumvire (Abu Jahl), ahubwo ujye wubama (usenga) uniyegereze Allah"
  97,1,"Mu by’ukuri, (iyi Qur’an) twayihishuye mu ijoro ry’igeno"
  97,2,Ni iki cyakumenyesha ijoro ry’igeno
  97,3,Ijoro ry’igeno riruta amezi igihumbi (ibyiza bikozwe muri iryo joro birusha ibihembo ibikozwe mu gihe kingana n’amezi igihumbi)
  97,4,"Abamalayika na Roho (Malayika Jibril) barimanukanamo babiherewe uburenganzira na Nyagasani wabo, bazanye (amategeko agenga) buri kintu cyose"
  97,5,Iryo (joro ryose) riba ryuje amahoro (n’impuhwe za Allah ku bagaragu be) kugeza umuseke utambitse
  98,1,"Babandi bahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo ndetse n’ababangikanyamana, ntibashobora kureka ubuhakanyi (bwabo) kugeza bagezweho n’ikimenyetso kigaragara"
  98,2,"(Icyo kimenyetso ni) Intumwa (Muhamadi) iturutse kwa Allah, ibasomera inyandiko zejejwe (Qur’an)"
  98,3,Zikubiyemo inkuru n’amategeko bitunganye
  98,4,"Kandi abahawe igitabo bacitsemo ibice nyuma y’uko bagezweho n’ikimenyetso kigaragara (kuko mbere y’uko Intumwa Muhamadi ihabwa ubutumwa, bose bayemeranyagaho kuko yari yarahanuwe mu bitabo byabo, ariko imaze kuza bamwe barayihakana)"
  98,5,"Kandi (no mu bitabo byabo) nta kindi bari barategetswe kitari ugusenga Allah bamwiyegurira, bahozaho amasengesho, ndetse bakanatanga amaturo. Iryo ni ryo dini ritunganye"
  98,6,"Mu by’ukuri, abahakanye bo mu bahawe igitabo ndetse n’ababangi- kanyamana bazaba mu muriro wa Jahanamu ubuziraherezo; abo ni bo babi mu biremwa"
  98,7,Naho abemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza; abo ni bo beza mu biremwa
  98,8,"Ibihembo byabo kwa Nyagasani wabo bizaba Ijuru rihoraho, ritembamo imigezi; (iryo Juru) bazaribamo ubuziraherezo. Allah yarabishimiye na bo baramwishimira. Ibyo (bihembo) ni iby’utinya Nyagasani we"
  99,1,Ubwo isi izatigiswa n’umutingito ukomeye
  99,2,Nuko isi igasohora ibiyirimo (abapfuye)
  99,3,"Umuntu azavuga ati \"Ese noneho (isi) yabaye iki"
  99,4,Uwo munsi (isi) izavuga inkuru zayo (z’ibyayibereyeho)
  99,5,Kubera ko Nyagasani wawe azaba yayibitegetse
  99,6,"Kuri uwo munsi, abantu bazasohoka (mu mva) batatanye kugira ngo berekwe ibikorwa byabo"
  99,7,"Icyo gihe uzaba yarakoze icyiza gifite uburemere bungana n’akantu gato cyane kurusha ibindi, azakibona (agihemberwe)"
  99,8,"N’uzaba yarakoze ikibi gifite uburemere bungana n’akantu gato cyane kurusha ibindi, azakibona (agihanirwe)"
  100,1,Ndahiriye ku mafarasi yiruka cyane avuza imirindi
  100,2,Akubita (ibinono) bigatarutsa ibishashi by’umuriro
  100,3,No ku mafarasi agaba igitero mu rukerera
  100,4,Akanatumura umukungugu
  100,5,Akinjira hagati mu ngabo z’umwanzi
  100,6,"Mu by’ukuri, umuntu ni indashima kuri Nyagasani we"
  100,7,Kandi rwose ibyo yabibera umuhamya
  100,8,Ndetse akunda imitungo bikabije